      <p>(c) are not yet in a position to use internal models for the purpose of calculating the own funds requirement for commodities risk.</p>
      <p>Institutions shall notify the use they make of this Article to their competent authorities together with evidence of their efforts to implement an internal model for the purpose of calculating the own funds requirement for commodities risk.</p>
